# Try to extract the table of contents or section headers to find the synthetic data/task generation section
import re
section_headers = []
for i, page in enumerate(reader.pages):
    text = page.extract_text()
    if text:
        # Look for lines that look like section headers
        matches = re.findall(r'^[0-9]+\.? ?[A-Z][A-Za-z ]+$', text, re.MULTILINE)
        section_headers.extend([(i, m) for m in matches])

section_headers
